    text: "Dr Nate has a comprehensive and thorough process that has fixed some stubborn shoulder pain. I couldn't recommend Dr Nate enough to those who are needing relief from pain. He has given me some helpful exercises to rehabilitate my rotator cuff which has made exercising more enjoyable again!",
